"title": "4336: iron",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4336",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Iron ore is mined from the earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:2\">JOB 28:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:9\">DEU 8:7–8:9</a></p>\n<h2>Iron ore is refined by smelting in a furnace</h2>\n<h3>Such imagery is often used of God's testing of his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:20\">EZK 22:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:21-Num31:23\">NUM 31:21–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:27-Jer6:29\">JER 6:27–6:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:18\">EZK 22:18</a></p>\n<h3>Egypt is described as an iron-smelting furnace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:20\">DEU 4:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:51\">1KI 8:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:4\">JER 11:4</a></p>\n<h2>Iron was a valuable metal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:6-Josh22:8\">JOS 22:6–22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:17\">ISA 60:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:12\">EZK 27:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:19\">EZK 27:19</a></p>\n<h2>Iron was prized for its great strength</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:40-Dan2:43\">DAN 2:40–2:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:19\">LEV 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:23\">DEU 28:23</a>JOB <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut40:15-Deut40:18\">40:15–40:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:27\">JOB 41:27</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:9\">2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:27\">REV 2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15\">REV 19:15</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:4\">ISA 48:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:18\">JER 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:12\">JER 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:31-Dan2:35\">DAN 2:31–2:35</a>DAN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:7\">7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:19\">DAN 7:19</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:13\">MIC 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Iron objects were taken as booty in war</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:15-Josh6:19\">JOS 6:15–6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:8\">JOS 22:8</a></p>\n<h2>Iron was used in the construction of the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2\">1CH 29:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14-1Chr22:16\">1CH 22:14–22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:7\">1CH 29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:12\">2CH 24:12</a></p>\n<h2>Other uses of iron</h2>\n<h3>For tools</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:22\">GEN 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:5\">DEU 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:30-Josh8:31\">JOS 8:30–8:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:31\">2SA 12:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:3\">1CH 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:7\">2SA 23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:7\">1KI 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:5-2Kgs6:6\">2KI 6:5–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23-Job19:24\">JOB 19:23–19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:2\">1TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>For chains, shackles and fetters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:18\">PSA 105:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:10\">PSA 107:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:6-Ps149:9\">PSA 149:6–149:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:15\">DAN 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:23\">DAN 4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:1-Mark5:4\">MRK 5:1–5:4</a></p>\n<h3>For chariots</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:19\">JDG 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh17:15-Josh17:18\">JOS 17:15–17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:2-Judg4:3\">JDG 4:2–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:12-Judg4:13\">JDG 4:12–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>For gates and gate fittings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:10\">ACT 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:25\">DEU 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:3\">1CH 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:15-Ps107:16\">PSA 107:15–107:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:2\">ISA 45:2</a></p>\n<h3>For weapons and armour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:16\">NUM 35:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:24\">JOB 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:9\">REV 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>For idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:4\">DAN 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a></p>\n<h3>For yokes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:48\">DEU 28:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:13-Jer28:14\">JER 28:13–28:14</a></p>\n<h3>For horns</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:11\">1KI 22:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:10\">2CH 18:10</a></p>\n<h3>For cooking utensils</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:3\">EZK 4:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>For a bed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:11\">DEU 3:11</a></strong></p>",
